headline: Keurig launches K-Cup ‘price lock event’ to help consumers avoid rising coffee costs
summary: With tariffs expected to further raise prices, beverage companies are playing up affordability to retain customers.

headline: Fidelity Select Consumer Staples Portfolio Q1 2025 Review
summary: For the quarter, Fidelity Select Consumer Staples Portfolio's Retail Class shares gained 0.65%, lagging the 4.11% advance of the MSCI U.S. IMI Consumer Staples 25/50 Index.
